author: COMSOL
description: This example simulates the effect of elastic and plastic deformations on pipeline corrosion. The Solid Mechanics interface with small strain plasticity model is used for elasto-plastic stress simulation. The Secondary Current Distribution interface is used to model electrochemical reactions. It is seen that pipeline corrosion accelerates with increase in longitudinal strain in the plastic deformation region.
